                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-05-19</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">余英时评新儒家那篇谦逊中有讽刺。对比郭沫若的那本揭露了郭之无行。钱穆的信尤其耐读</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1184233862">
